Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.18,0:00:03.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在这世界上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.74,0:00:06.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有着由善意而生的恶意
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.31,0:00:08.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由恶意而生的善意
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.63,0:00:11.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修所引起的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.56,0:00:14.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟应该归于哪类呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.21,0:00:18.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,审判是世界的必然吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.42,0:00:19.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Geass
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.79,0:00:23.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,使用这非人类力量的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.62,0:00:26.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,会逐渐感受到心灵的孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.62,0:00:29.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,坠入善意与恶意的狭缝中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.52,0:00:30.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然而
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.69,0:00:34.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有人能从中站起来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.76,0:00:36.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.78,0:00:40.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人毋庸置疑将获得成为帝王的资格吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.92,0:02:16.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fad(600,0)\pos(424,395)}STAGE 15
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.52,0:02:16.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fad(600,0)\pos(424,430)}喝彩的毛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.34,0:02:18.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,首先想确认一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.12,0:02:22.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是我的敌人 还是伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.11,0:02:23.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到现在还说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.86,0:02:26.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个叫毛的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.58,0:02:29.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有着可以看透别人想法的Geass
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.72,0:02:31.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可以这样理解吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.16,0:02:31.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.46,0:02:35.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Geass的表现形式和它的拥有者有关
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.17,0:02:37.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就毛来说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.43,0:02:41.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,集中思想的话最远可以读出500米左右距离内的思考
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.96,0:02:44.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他想要的话还能读出深层意识
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.81,0:02:48.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对于使用脑子作战的你来说是最麻烦的敌人了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.35,0:02:49.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,500米
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.40,0:02:52.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然已经想象过了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.52,0:02:55.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,除我以外还存在着能使用Geass的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.07,0:02:57.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙也和你缔结了契约吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.32,0:02:59.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在11年以前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.12,0:03:02.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原来还是大前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.31,0:03:03.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.10,0:03:05.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个大前辈是我的敌人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.51,0:03:07.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,毛的目的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.16,0:03:09.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然说是敌人 但是不至于以性命为目标…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.66,0:03:10.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.19,0:03:15.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话只要把ZERO的身份告诉军队和警察就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.74,0:03:17.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是却只对莎莉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.86,0:03:19.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙的能力条件是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.84,0:03:22.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,毛的Geass很强
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.56,0:03:27.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不像你一样有使用次数和要直接见到对方眼睛的限制
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.37,0:03:29.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没有弱点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.81,0:03:31.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,硬要说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.07,0:03:33.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,毛无法停止他的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.52,0:03:36.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总是听到周围人心里的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.74,0:03:39.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不论本人是否想听到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.64,0:04:04.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道啊 毛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.99,0:04:06.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧 毛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.74,0:04:08.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.79,0:04:09.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,毛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.90,0:04:12.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,毛你起来了吗 毛…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.69,0:04:15.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,C.C. 果然非你不可
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.37,0:04:17.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等着吧 我现在就去见你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.90,0:04:22.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果毛读出了我的思考的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.34,0:04:25.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定会瞄准我最大的弱点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.55,0:04:28.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好久没有和哥哥单独在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.90,0:04:31.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有时也该让{\fnDFPHSGothic-W5\fe128\fs25\b1\alpha&H15&}咲{\r}世子休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.14,0:04:35.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,从今天开始一段时间我会留在家里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.29,0:04:38.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥最近总是离开家里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.99,0:04:41.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是找到了什么有趣的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.84,0:04:42.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.66,0:04:45.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这次的对手有点麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.17,0:04:49.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能被哥哥这么说到底是什么人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.84,0:04:52.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,继修耐泽尔哥哥之后是第一个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.19,0:04:56.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.29,0:04:58.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没有许可证不能卖给你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.15,0:05:00.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且客人你是中华联邦的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.38,0:05:03.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可是你却卖给黑色骑士团的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.15,0:05:06.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,上周二的23点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.44,0:05:08.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对方的名字是沃尔夫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.40,0:05:09.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这当然是化名
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.52,0:05:11.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.72,0:05:13.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你能给我行一点方便啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.91,0:05:15.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在很多方面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.47,0:05:17.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.81,0:05:21.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,保护你的妹妹的确是必要的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.01,0:05:22.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但光是等着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.55,0:05:24.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,让黑色骑士团开始寻找了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.76,0:05:28.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他不在贫民区而在这东京租界的话怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.51,0:05:29.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是浪费时间而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.88,0:05:32.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,比起这个还不如把我当成诱饵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.16,0:05:34.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,毛的目的是我 我去…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.72,0:05:36.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 如果一直使用Geass的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.69,0:05:38.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也会变成那样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.39,0:05:40.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.37,0:05:43.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为没有完成和你的契约而变成了那样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.80,0:05:47.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要使用下去 总有一天Geass的力量就会爆发
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.33,0:05:51.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,无法克服的人就会被自己的那种力量所吞噬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.71,0:05:53.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你明明知道会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.18,0:05:54.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,却还提出要缔结契约吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.00,0:05:56.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对我 还有对毛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.49,0:05:57.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.48,0:05:59.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是狠心的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.28,0:06:01.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还真是不考虑被迫签契约的人的心情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.32,0:06:04.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,毛没能完成契约
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.82,0:06:06.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以被抛弃了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.13,0:06:10.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,契约的内容是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.48,0:06:12.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是卑劣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.84,0:06:16.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抛弃他的时候为什么没有解决他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.18,0:06:18.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夺走力量 夺走性命
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.21,0:06:21.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是因为你做事半吊子莎莉才…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.66,0:06:27.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对付毛还是采取分头行动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.84,0:06:29.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天开始我搬到隔壁的房间去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.76,0:06:30.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,隔壁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.23,0:06:33.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是学生会和文化部的部室
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.23,0:06:34.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那种事我不管
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.47,0:06:36.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,事后处理你来想办法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.33,0:06:42.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,医疗检查
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.73,0:06:45.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对KnightMare的驾驶员来说这是义务
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.84,0:06:46.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.64,0:06:49.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就明天学校放学以后
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.63,0:06:50.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.43,0:06:51.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 塞希尔小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.70,0:06:54.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有见到由菲米娅皇女殿下的方法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.98,0:06:56.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你想见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.76,0:06:58.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.02,0:07:00.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谒见必须是骑士侯以上才行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.67,0:07:03.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,伯爵阁下您应该有办法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.51,0:07:04.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.40,0:07:05.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.61,0:07:09.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,罗伊德是伯爵吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.37,0:07:12.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.24,0:07:13.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的贵族
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.55,0:07:16.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是搞不清游戏和工作的区别
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.12,0:07:16.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.59,0:07:19.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要几天就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.03,0:07:23.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能在这段时间禁止别人进入俱乐部的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.93,0:07:25.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这虽然不是不能办到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.09,0:07:28.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 难道你是皇子的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.54,0:07:29.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没有暴露
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.43,0:07:32.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知道我还活着这件事的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.27,0:07:33.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只有阿修佛德家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.81,0:07:34.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修佛德啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.21,0:07:37.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.47,0:07:38.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.68,0:07:40.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我又要去相亲了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.74,0:07:43.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这次可能逃不掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.06,0:07:44.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 我该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.83,0:07:46.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呀 这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.27,0:07:49.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,会长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.57,0:07:51.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,莎莉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.63,0:07:53.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你恢复晨练了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.20,0:07:53.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.99,0:07:55.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,从今天开始的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.18,0:07:56.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也不能一直消沉着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.68,0:07:59.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也该向你学习啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.23,0:08:00.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你的行动力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.98,0:08:02.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.26,0:08:03.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,会长你才…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.33,0:08:06.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 你是上次的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.07,0:08:08.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是我们学校的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.73,0:08:10.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.33,0:08:11.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是同班的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.86,0:08:14.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.47,0:08:17.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,够了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.66,0:08:19.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,莎莉 要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.29,0:08:21.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在就来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.27,0:08:22.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 再见会长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.73,0:08:23.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.45,0:08:26.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那个是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.78,0:08:28.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是吵架了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.53,0:08:30.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才装的不认识吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.60,0:08:32.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是可爱的游戏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.89,0:08:34.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思可以帮忙配合一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.07,0:08:36.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,直到她的热情冷却为止
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.87,0:08:38.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.33,0:08:39.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,会很长吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.49,0:08:41.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 可能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.11,0:08:47.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是说了我在找的不是Refrain的卖家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.01,0:08:50.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而是叫毛的东洋人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.87,0:08:52.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在租界说到东洋人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.75,0:08:54.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的就只有那些打杂的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.97,0:08:56.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,去找警察吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.98,0:08:58.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我讨厌警察
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.73,0:09:00.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么拜托黑色骑士团吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.98,0:09:03.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,内部途径的话不论租界和贫民区
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.40,0:09:05.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在他们是最强的了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.43,0:09:07.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是谁都是一样的回答
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.60,0:09:08.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是当然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.86,0:09:12.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.45,0:09:14.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.82,0:09:16.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,从刚才开始你在找什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.20,0:09:19.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,日记 我的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.34,0:09:20.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,找不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.92,0:09:23.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没有带到外面去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.19,0:09:24.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.09,0:09:32.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 很对不起 ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.40,0:09:34.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,关于叫毛的男人到现在为止
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.08,0:09:34.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.16,0:09:37.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要使用京都的情报网吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.24,0:09:38.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.06,0:09:39.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,关东地区就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.70,0:09:41.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他如果进网的话再联系我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.89,0:09:42.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.82,0:09:44.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 下个定时联络见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.49,0:09:50.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,进入500米以内的话会被毛读到内心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.55,0:09:54.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这也可以成为预知他下一步要走什么的条件
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.32,0:09:58.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要将军的话还缺一个棋子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.52,0:09:59.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不够吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.67,0:10:03.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看来我们考虑的事是一样的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.16,0:10:05.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.67,0:10:08.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想我们可以合作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.62,0:10:09.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.90,0:10:17.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.21,0:10:19.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是我 鲁路
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.17,0:10:22.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,C.C.在那儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.39,0:10:25.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想和她单独谈 换她接
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.25,0:10:33.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.34,0:10:34.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.72,0:10:38.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会倒在那儿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.80,0:10:40.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你的名字叫什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.48,0:10:41.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.36,0:10:43.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,名字
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.62,0:10:45.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,叫什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.54,0:10:47.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道 你的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.44,0:10:51.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,关于ZERO的事 那时你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.11,0:10:52.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.89,0:10:55.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.45,0:10:56.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,做像是叛变的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.98,0:10:57.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,却变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.18,0:10:59.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.26,0:11:02.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么也
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.51,0:11:03.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.47,0:11:07.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然能闭着眼睛帮你脱下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.21,0:11:08.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但穿上…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.92,0:11:10.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是房间很暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.95,0:11:11.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,应该不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.22,0:11:14.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.41,0:11:18.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总之好像被好人救了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.18,0:11:23.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,高兴吧 鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.73,0:11:26.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我和你就在这儿告别了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.66,0:11:29.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想和毛重修旧好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.26,0:11:30.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你想背叛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.47,0:11:31.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到现在还说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.47,0:11:34.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有把你当作同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.19,0:11:36.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只是共犯而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.10,0:11:37.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.28,0:11:40.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是让人吃惊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.78,0:11:42.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你这不是和毛一样了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.04,0:11:48.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,C.C.你对我的情况知道得太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.25,0:11:50.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能让你就这么走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.21,0:11:53.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.63,0:11:55.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,留在我的身边 C.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.87,0:12:02.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Geass对我不起作用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.00,0:12:04.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.63,0:12:06.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.75,0:12:08.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有打算说出你的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.72,0:12:11.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Geass也留给你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.75,0:12:15.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,毛也不会再出现在你的眼前了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.69,0:12:17.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来阻碍就消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.69,0:12:18.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.84,0:12:19.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.61,0:12:31.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,检查的结果良好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.86,0:12:36.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然规律与生命的项目数值看起来有点偏高
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.92,0:12:38.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,会有问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.83,0:12:40.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,作为军人来说是优秀的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.14,0:12:45.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是否无意识的把自己和父亲比较
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.86,0:12:48.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定那个在约束着你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.02,0:12:52.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是拥有有名父母的孩子常有的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.55,0:12:53.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,枢木玄武
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.89,0:12:55.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原日本国首相
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.72,0:12:57.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎是一个了不起的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.57,0:13:00.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好慢啊 浦部他们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.02,0:13:03.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来还真是个讽刺的碰头地点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.02,0:13:06.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,枢木首相的慰灵碑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.45,0:13:10.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,才刚决定彻底抗争就立刻自杀的卖国贼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.65,0:13:11.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别这样说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.68,0:13:12.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再这样说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.00,0:13:15.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等于是也否定了自杀的片濑少将
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.92,0:13:19.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,发现潜伏中的藤堂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.81,0:13:21.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,各班捕获准备
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.37,0:13:22.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes My Lord
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.02,0:13:26.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经看过了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.49,0:13:28.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,黑色骑士团的再编成方案
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.73,0:13:32.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然有几个想要修正的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.12,0:13:33.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但大致上我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.81,0:13:36.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你的想法我也会传达给扇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.29,0:13:37.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.74,0:13:40.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把发展声望作为要点的设想与归纳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.32,0:13:42.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望你能把它放到下一次的观点中去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.76,0:13:43.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.86,0:13:46.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是最后的考验吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.14,0:13:48.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,迪哈鲁特
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.80,0:13:50.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然是布里塔尼亚人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.31,0:13:51.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但比预想中还要有能力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.30,0:13:55.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然还不能完全排除间谍的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.06,0:13:59.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 毛的电话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.22,0:14:21.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,C.C. 你是多么的安静啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.41,0:14:23.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只有你的心理无法读取
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.16,0:14:26.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然你是最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.76,0:14:28.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还是一样的孩子气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.69,0:14:31.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你说我是白马王子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.42,0:14:33.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是来接你的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.35,0:14:38.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很高兴吧 C.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.26,0:14:38.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,毛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.25,0:14:40.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以前我应该就说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.80,0:14:42.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我和你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.30,0:14:43.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那种事是骗人的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.04,0:14:46.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,C.C.最喜欢我了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.32,0:14:48.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 毛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.14,0:14:50.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,毛  毛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.59,0:14:51.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.60,0:14:52.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.32,0:14:55.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.46,0:14:57.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要倾听我的声音就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.16,0:15:00.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.90,0:15:03.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只听不到我心中声音的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.70,0:15:06.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,两个人独处的时候才能平静的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.89,0:15:09.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我总是会在你身边的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.40,0:15:13.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 我就在这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.13,0:15:15.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以安心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.18,0:15:18.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,C.C. 只有你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.45,0:15:20.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想得到的只有你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.89,0:15:22.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修那种人随他去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.58,0:15:23.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你能来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.27,0:15:24.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.92,0:15:31.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一开始就应该这样做的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.47,0:15:35.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是我C.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.17,0:15:36.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,毛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.59,0:15:39.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我在克洛维斯游乐场等你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.37,0:15:40.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你一个人来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.52,0:15:43.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还是老样子的自我主义啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.91,0:15:47.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你不来的话只会让我暴露鲁路修的身份哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.43,0:15:49.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然随时能抹杀掉他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.06,0:15:52.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,高兴吧 鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.56,0:15:54.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我和你就在这儿告别了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.97,0:15:57.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.36,0:15:59.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,随便的回来又离开
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.02,0:16:02.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,自我主义的女人真是难以理解啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.63,0:16:04.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.13,0:16:08.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然C.C.无法向我开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.88,0:16:11.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,C.C.是喜欢我的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.41,0:16:14.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.04,0:16:16.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是利用你而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.10,0:16:18.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.40,0:16:20.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说谎可不好 说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.87,0:16:24.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说谎是不行的 说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.59,0:16:27.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.45,0:16:29.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.60,0:16:34.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,C.C. 我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.91,0:16:37.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在澳大利亚建了房子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.65,0:16:40.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,白色而干净的十分安静的屋子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.54,0:16:46.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是去澳大利亚一定得乘飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.37,0:16:51.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是要把C.C.放进飞机里的话太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.95,0:16:53.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.49,0:16:57.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把你分成小块
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.05,0:17:00.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话很快就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.97,0:17:04.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是对我的惩罚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.36,0:17:06.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.27,0:17:09.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不对不对不对不对不对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.53,0:17:11.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是感谢的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.73,0:17:13.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然在那儿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.86,0:17:17.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别人的声音不会打扰的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.69,0:17:19.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,位置就被特定在这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.85,0:17:20.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.76,0:17:25.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你的Geass的有效距离最大为500米
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.61,0:17:27.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,无法到达这个东京塔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.29,0:17:30.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,的确 的确
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.03,0:17:31.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.90,0:17:34.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,即便这样 你想怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.34,0:17:37.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然你很卖力的做了很多入侵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.46,0:17:40.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想要远程操作别的玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.34,0:17:41.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来对付我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.16,0:17:45.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说用你那能说会道的嘴来说服我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.22,0:17:49.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 这次是不出声了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.82,0:17:51.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果想要C.C.的话你也
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.01,0:17:57.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,毛 你不会认为C.C.是她真正的名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.86,0:18:04.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.65,0:18:06.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她真正的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.94,0:18:09.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吗C.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.95,0:18:11.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明明没有告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.57,0:18:14.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么对那种家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.27,0:18:17.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道了吧 C.C.是我的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.24,0:18:21.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,C.C.是我的人啊 毛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.51,0:18:22.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.43,0:18:24.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不对不对不对不对不对不对
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.90,0:18:27.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,从很久以前开始她就只是我的C.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.92,0:18:30.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经得到了C.C.的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.77,0:18:33.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还包括你从来没有见过的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.49,0:18:35.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.44,0:18:37.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.30,0:18:40.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,滚出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.80,0:18:41.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.44,0:18:44.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来这儿 到我的面前来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.44,0:18:45.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把你剁碎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.04,0:18:49.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个 骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.45,0:18:51.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,毛 是你输了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.13,0:18:54.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.72,0:18:56.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行了 我会和C.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.25,0:19:07.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.11,0:19:09.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是距离
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.72,0:19:13.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.25,0:19:14.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.15,0:19:16.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,丢掉武器投降
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.50,0:19:18.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事 这些家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.43,0:19:21.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,通告绑架犯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.11,0:19:23.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,丢掉武器投降
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.38,0:19:25.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,警察
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.01,0:19:28.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁通报的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.23,0:19:36.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.22,0:19:38.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会在这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.43,0:19:39.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.55,0:19:41.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚才明明还在东京塔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.92,0:19:44.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是笨蛋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.60,0:19:46.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那些都是录象
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.96,0:19:47.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.29,0:19:50.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明明还和我对话的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.08,0:19:53.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你的思考太容易猜透了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.31,0:19:55.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我虽然读不了心但还是猜对了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.58,0:19:57.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把我的回答预测出来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.12,0:19:59.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别开玩笑了 你这个小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.17,0:20:01.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算被警察抓到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.78,0:20:03.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也能很快的出来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.27,0:20:04.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.29,0:20:06.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙疯了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.59,0:20:08.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙真奇怪 把武器扔掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.63,0:20:10.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正如通报的一样 像是Refrain中毒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.87,0:20:14.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了 别说我的坏话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.55,0:20:17.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,C.C.告诉我了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.82,0:20:19.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你无法停止你的Geass
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.98,0:20:23.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是有效范围要看你的集中力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.15,0:20:25.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为了分散我的注意力而使用了屏幕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.18,0:20:30.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我还有赢你的办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.84,0:20:33.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,当你这么做的时候也就是你的最后了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.16,0:20:35.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.40,0:20:36.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好好说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.73,0:20:37.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么最后啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.39,0:20:40.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,警察们 好好听着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.65,0:20:43.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那边的家伙是恐怖分子的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.25,0:20:43.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.83,0:20:48.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,毛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.69,0:20:52.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.64,0:20:57.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,缔结契约时
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.13,0:21:01.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,毛才6岁 又是孤儿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.92,0:21:07.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,读书写字 父母的爱 善恶全都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.36,0:21:08.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是ECORE-3
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.57,0:21:10.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,按照预定在贫民区解放了人质
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.73,0:21:13.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 病院的搬送怎么…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.80,0:21:15.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我所赐予他的Geass的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.08,0:21:17.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,让毛和别人疏远了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.84,0:21:24.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我成了毛的好友兼恋人和无关的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.95,0:21:28.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对于毛来说只有我是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.23,0:21:31.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是世界的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.32,0:21:34.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,C.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.94,0:21:36.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会输给Geass
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.24,0:21:39.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我会支配这个力量来掌握它
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.34,0:21:42.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,会改变这个世界给你看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.35,0:21:46.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的愿望和你的愿望我全部都会实现
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.12,0:21:50.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙没能完成的契约由我来实现
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.22,0:21:51.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.01,0:21:52.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.22,0:21:55.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是抚慰吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.71,0:21:56.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怜悯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.30,0:21:59.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说是执着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.02,0:22:03.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是契约
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.68,0:22:06.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这次是由我对你提出的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.98,0:22:08.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.54,0:22:11.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,缔结吧 这个契约
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.62,0:23:51.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在是前进的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.35,0:23:53.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,见到科奈莉娅 得到事情的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.67,0:23:56.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然后制造出娜娜莉生活的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.58,0:23:59.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小的战场已经没有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.30,0:24:01.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要把东京租界制压下来
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.35,0:24:03.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为了这样要增强军事力量
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.81,0:24:05.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还要利用外部势力
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.78,0:24:08.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能够利用的棋子全部都要利用
